<a class="title" href="/nodes/96861/comments/1418898">Re: grep</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/barmic" rel="author">Barret Michel</a> <time class="updated" datetime="2012-12-27T16:32:13+01:00"><span class="date">le 27/12/12</span> <span class="time">à 16:32</span></time>.
