<li class="comment even score4" id="comment-1419024">
<h2>
<a class="parent" href="/news/grabuge-a-la-fsf-gnutls-quitte-le-projet-gnu-et-sed-et-grep-perdent-leur-mainteneur#comment-1418745" title="Aller au commentaire parent">[^]</a>
